Some days, even postpone to transmit soccer instead. I pay the F1 TV PRO but cant have any livestream due to Globo tv rights. I hope on the next tv agreement in brazil, f1 decides to be able o stream all content. Much better the f1 professionals commenting the race than some soccer experts that know nothing about racing.
